What you need to know:

Well, just days after Harambee Stars’ hopes of playing with the big boys in the continental Holy Grail went up in smoke, the team has rekindled its World Cup dreamsIf you know anything about Kenyan football, then you would know that all this excited chatter on social media about Kenya being serious contenders for a ticket to next year’s World Cup is cheap talkKenya failed to make the cut in a 24-team Africa Cup of Nations tournament, how on earth will they secure one of Africa’s five tickets to Qatar?